Content:
itn3000 added support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2526] multiple variables in 
``with-env``
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2530] tables for multiple variables in 
``with-env``
thegedge fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2525] path completions with 
``cd``
, improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2503] completions for 
``~``
, and additional 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2498] completion fixes
gillespiecd cleaned up some of the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2522] duration conversions
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2507] cpu time to 
``ps -l``
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2496] number of links column in 
``ls -l``
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2517] updated dependencies
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2520] removed unused dependences
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2502] weather symbols to 
``char``
jonathandturner added support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2509] decimals as range boundaries
, improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2506] range parsing
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2505] modulo operator and renamed 
``in``
 and 
``not-in``
ritobanrc added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2508] ``each windows``
 and 
``each group``
 for working with multiple rows at a time
defstryker improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2499] ranges for substrings
almindor added support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2495] ``exec``
andrasio updated the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/book/pull/131] Spanish introduction chapter of the book
 and 
